This directory contains a set of tests which can be carried out when
calling:

$ make check

The test go through prepared test suite and perform various checks
against classes.

To enable, use --enable-testing on configure:
./configure --enable-testing

Requirements:

 1. CppUnit
    Homepage: http://cppunit.sourceforge.net/
    Cookbook: http://cppunit.sourceforge.net/doc/lastest/cppunit_cookbook.html

 2. Mockpp
    Homepage: http://mockpp.sourceforge.net/
    